<template>
  <label>{{ label }}</label>
  <input
    v-bind:value="inputValue"
    v-on:input="$emit('input', $event.target.value)"
    type="text"
  />
</template>
<script>
export default {
  name: "MisaInput",
 props: ['value', 'label', 'inputValue'],
  methods: {},

  data() {
    return {
      firstName: "",
      lastName: "",
      firstNameLabel: "First Name",
      lastNameLabel: "Last Name",
    };
  },
  computed: {
    computedFirstName: {
      get() {
        return this.firstName;
      },
      set(value) {
        this.firstName = value;
      },
    },
    computedLastName: {
      get() {
        return this.lastName;
      },
      set(value) {
        this.lastName = value;
      },
    },
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
